question: Tī si nî-tau ê 'bē sī CIB chāi-gōa ê net interest income' siōng koân?
2014 ni koseng 2016 ni koseng, CIB Markets Net Interest Income, tan-chiok-bán ê ti thun? (millions)
2015 nî, sîn seng-li̍t ê chu-kim sîⁿ-tāi siōng-kē ê tōa hong-bīn ê net interest yield sī siáⁿ jī?
Chiu-chāi 2014 chì 2016, 'bô-hōe CIB chhī-liû cheng-seng sòaⁿ ê tiong-kun liâⁿ-siat lōe-sòe' ê piàn-tōaⁿ sī án-chóaⁿ-iūⁿ ê?
answer: Bô-hōe CIB chhī-liû cheng-seng sòaⁿ ê tiong-kun liâⁿ-siat lōe-sòe chiân-chē kàng chiūⁿ 2.53% tī 2014 nî kàu 2.49% tī 2015 nî, chiánhⁿ tit tio̍h chi̍t ê chin tōa ê cheng-tióng kàu 2.59% tī 2016 nî, kiat-sok che tiáⁿ-á ê sî-chūn, tit-tio̍h i siāng koân ê tiám.

question: Liām chhut 'net interest income 2013 managed basis' chhiau-kòe 45,000 pah bān ê nî-tōaⁿ.
Tī 2016 nî, siánn-mih phiah-sò͘ sī chha-put-toā 'sîng-pún lâi the̍h-tit ê tài-sán' ê 'chha-put-toā thàu-chè teng-chiam ê tài-sán' tah chò?

Tōa-su tōa-su, nā Net Interest Income sī Net Interest Yield hām Average Interest-Earning Assets ê sán-phín, án-choáⁿ 2014 nî ê 'cib markets net interest income' ē-sī siáⁿ-choáⁿ-iūⁿ nā i ê yield sī 1.25 lâi-tùi 1.15? (Siong-tōa-su lîn-bûn)

Tùi sann-ê nî-khuá, kiám-chhiáⁿ "iáⁿ-liâu chu-kim sêng-pún chu-sìn ê chu-sìn” ê cheng-tióng kah “tâi-tōa chu-kim sêng-pún chu-sìn ê chu-sìn ê net interest yield 2013 managed basis” ê piàn-hòa chi-kan ê koan-hē ūi-tio̍h.
answer: Bô sî-tiâu-khí-lâi ê ti̍t-chiap koan-liân. 2014 nî kàu 2015 nî, t tổng iáⁿ-liâu chu-kim sêng-pún chu-sìn cheng-tióng, tān-sī net interest yield kiám-sió. Put-kò, 2015 nî kàu 2016 nî, nn̄g-ê chu-sìn kah yield lóng cheng-tióng. Chit-ê hui-tēⁿ-tēⁿ ê koan-hē, su-iàu kóng ū kî-thaⁿ ê iáⁿ-chāi khah tiōng-iàu tùi net interest yield chhâi ū éng-hiáng.

question: Tī chiah khu thiam lāi-bīn, ū nn̄g-ê tiâu-bo̍k ê bô͘-koân hiòng-tē chū-siá ê iáⁿ-bīn sī chòe-chòe-chū-chúi cheng-ka hō͘ chìn-chêng ê chóng-sò͘?
answer: less : cib markets net interest income ( c )
less : average cib markets interest-earning assets ( c )

question: Na yi-tang ê 'cib markets net interest income' khah tōa ê nî-kî-tōa-nî piāⁿ-tōaⁿ (tō sī tōa-ê ia̍h-sī sió-ê) ê chha-pia̍t?
Nai nî chòe khoài hō͘ cheⁿ-chha̍t siu-ji̍t siāng chē?
